lead_paragraph: England are waiting on the result of an x-ray to Maro Itoje, who is a doubt for the autumn internationals after injuring his hand in Saracens' Champions Cup win over Scarlets on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Itoje Injury Adds to England Woe
